<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>بابٌ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>رُبَّمَا أقامت العربُ ما هو من الشيء مَقَامَهُ،<span class="c5"> قال الرَّاجِز:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَلو تَرَى إذْ جُبَّتِي مِنْ طَاقِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَلِمَّتِي مِثْلُ جَنَاحِ غَاقِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>تَخْفِقُ عِنْدَ المَشْيِ والسِّبَاقِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>أراد مثل جَنَاحِ غُرَابٍ فَأَقَامَ صَوْتَهُ مَقَامَهُ،<span class="c5"> ومثله:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>إِذَا عُقَيْلٌ عَقَدُوا الرَّايَاتِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَنَقَعَ الصُّرَاخُ بِالبَيَاتِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>أَبَوْا فَمَا يُعْطُونَ شَيئًا هَاتِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>أي قَائِلَ هَاتِ،<span class="c5"> ومثله:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>أَلَا إِنَّنِي شَرِبْتُ أَسْوَدَ حَالِكًا ... أَلَا بَجَلِي مِنَ الشَّرَابِ أَلا بَجَلْ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>يُرِيدُ سُمَّ أَسْوَدَ،<span class="c5"> ومثله:</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>إِذَا حَمَلْتُ بِزَّتِي عَلَى عَدَسْ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>عَلَى الَّتِي بَيْنَ الحِمَارِ وَالفَرَسْ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>